---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">The AURA Initiative</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            AURA (Attribution & Usage Reporting for AI) is an open protocol designed to ensure transparent and standardized reporting of AI-assisted content generation.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Declare AI involvement clearly in scientific and public work.</li>
            <li>Generate verifiable metadata for each AI-assisted contribution.</li>
            <li>Enable traceability and reproducibility through public identifiers.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Explore our <a href="/block" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">JSON block</a> for an example implementation.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
